Say '''Pontevedra''' et kumatlo ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Negros Occidental]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 47,945 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 112.5 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumatlo ya distrito. Say zip code to et 6105.	
															
